---
import RootLayout from '../../layouts/RootLayout.astro';
---

<RootLayout 
	title="Small Business Consulting in Lexington, KY - NOZA LLC" 
	description="Strategic business consulting for startups and small businesses in Lexington Kentucky. Business clarity, systems optimization, and growth strategies."
>
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="consulting-hero">
		<div class="cosmic-background">
			<div class="stars"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-1"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-2"></div>
			<div class="nebula nebula-3"></div>
		</div>

		<div class="particles"></div>

		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1 class="consulting-headline">Small Business Consulting in Lexington, KY</h1>
			<p class="consulting-subheadline">Strategic guidance that cuts through confusion and builds sustainable growth. We help Lexington small businesses get clear on direction, optimize operations, and scale profitably.</p>
			<div class="hero-pricing">
				<span class="price-badge">Flexible Engagement Models</span>
				<span class="price-subtext">From one-time strategy sessions to ongoing partnerships</span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Consulting Intro Section -->
	<section class="consulting-intro">
		<div class="intro-container">
			<h2 class="intro-title">Strategy + Execution = Real Growth</h2>
			<p class="intro-text">
				Most small business owners are talented at what they do—building great products, delivering excellent service. But strategy? Systems? That's different. That's where business consulting creates real value.
			</p>
			<p class="intro-text">
				We help you get clear on where you're going, build systems that scale, optimize what's already working, and avoid expensive mistakes. Our consulting is grounded in real-world experience, focused on outcomes, and designed specifically for Central Kentucky small businesses.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Consulting Services Section -->
	<section class="consulting-services">
		<div class="services-container">
			<h2 class="services-title">Our Consulting Services</h2>
			
			<div class="services-grid">
				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon startup-icon"></div>
					<h3>Startup & Launch Consulting</h3>
					<p>Starting a new business? We help you avoid the biggest pitfalls and build a solid foundation from day one.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Business model validation</li>
						<li>Go-to-market strategy</li>
						<li>Financial planning</li>
						<li>Legal structure guidance</li>
						<li>First-year roadmap</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon clarity-icon"></div>
					<h3>Business Clarity & Strategy</h3>
					<p>Get crystal clear on your vision, mission, and strategy. Many businesses operate without a coherent plan—that changes with us.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Vision & mission development</li>
						<li>Competitive analysis</li>
						<li>Market positioning</li>
						<li>3-5 year strategic plan</li>
						<li>KPI framework</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon systems-icon"></div>
					<h3>Operations & Systems</h3>
					<p>Chaos disguises itself as growth. We build systems that allow your business to scale without you working more hours.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Process documentation</li>
						<li>Workflow optimization</li>
						<li>Team structure design</li>
						<li>Standard operating procedures</li>
						<li>Technology stack review</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon marketing-icon"></div>
					<h3>Marketing Systems & Growth</h3>
					<p>Build a marketing machine that consistently generates leads. Strategy that actually integrates with your business model.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Customer acquisition strategy</li>
						<li>Marketing channel selection</li>
						<li>Sales funnel design</li>
						<li>Customer retention systems</li>
						<li>Growth metrics dashboard</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon finance-icon"></div>
					<h3>Financial Planning & Analysis</h3>
					<p>Understand your numbers. Build pricing that works. Forecast profitability. Make data-driven financial decisions.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Financial forecasting</li>
						<li>Pricing strategy</li>
						<li>Profitability analysis</li>
						<li>Cash flow management</li>
						<li>Financial benchmarking</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card-item">
					<div class="service-card-icon networking-icon"></div>
					<h3>Network & Vendor Connections</h3>
					<p>We connect you with trusted specialists—accountants, lawyers, contractors, service providers—so you don't have to figure it out alone.</p>
					<ul class="service-features">
						<li>Vendor introductions</li>
						<li>Strategic partnerships</li>
						<li>Professional network access</li>
						<li>Contractor recommendations</li>
						<li>Peer advisor group</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Who We Help Section -->
	<section class="who-we-help">
		<div class="help-container">
			<h2 class="help-title">Who We Help</h2>
			
			<div class="help-grid">
				<div class="help-card">
					<div class="help-icon founders"></div>
					<h3>Founders & Startup Owners</h3>
					<p>Building something new requires different thinking than operating an existing business. We provide founder-focused coaching and strategy.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="help-card">
					<div class="help-icon growing"></div>
					<h3>Growing Businesses (7-50 employees)</h3>
					<p>You've proven product-market fit. Now scale without losing your culture. Build systems that support rapid growth.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="help-card">
					<div class="help-icon plateau"></div>
					<h3>Businesses on a Plateau</h3>
					<p>Growth has stalled. Profitability isn't improving. Something needs to change. We help diagnose problems and create breakthrough strategies.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="help-card">
					<div class="help-icon transition"></div>
					<h3>Businesses in Transition</h3>
					<p>Ownership transition, market shifts, new competition—change requires strategy. We help you navigate uncertainty with confidence.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Outcomes Section -->
	<section class="consulting-outcomes">
		<div class="outcomes-container">
			<h2 class="outcomes-title">What Our Clients Achieve</h2>
			
			<div class="outcomes-grid">
				<div class="outcome-item">
					<div class="outcome-icon growth-up"></div>
					<h3>Revenue Growth</h3>
					<p>Clients typically see 20-40% revenue growth in year one through better strategy and execution</p>
				</div>

				<div class="outcome-item">
					<div class="outcome-icon profit-up"></div>
					<h3>Improved Profitability</h3>
					<p>Better pricing, optimized operations, and elimination of waste improve bottom-line results</p>
				</div>

				<div class="outcome-item">
					<div class="outcome-icon time-back"></div>
					<h3>Time Freedom</h3>
					<p>Systems and delegation mean business owners work less while company grows more</p>
				</div>

				<div class="outcome-item">
					<div class="outcome-icon confidence"></div>
					<h3>Strategic Clarity</h3>
					<p>Replace guesswork with confident, data-backed decisions about where to invest and how to grow</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Consulting Process Section -->
	<section class="consulting-process">
		<div class="process-container">
			<h2 class="process-title">Our Consulting Engagement</h2>
			<p class="process-subtitle">How we work with you</p>

			<div class="process-steps">
				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">01</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Discovery & Assessment</h3>
						<p>We dive deep into your business. Your goals, challenges, market, team, financials. We're not here to judge—we're here to understand and help.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-connector"></div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">02</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Strategy Development</h3>
						<p>We build a custom strategy tailored to your situation. Clear vision, realistic roadmap, measurable milestones. Nothing generic.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-connector"></div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">03</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Implementation Support</h3>
						<p>Strategy without execution is just ideas. We help you implement, stay accountable, and course-correct as needed.</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-connector"></div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">04</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Ongoing Guidance</h3>
						<p>Business changes constantly. We provide ongoing counsel, strategy refinement, and support as you scale and evolve.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Consulting FAQ Section -->
	<section class="consulting-faq">
		<div class="faq-header">
			<h2 class="faq-title">Consulting Questions Answered</h2>
			<p class="faq-subtitle">Everything you need to know about business consulting</p>
		</div>

		<div class="faq-container">
			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Who is business consulting for?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Consulting is for entrepreneurs and business owners who want to grow strategically. Whether you're starting a business, scaling from 5 to 50 employees, stuck on a plateau, or navigating a major transition—consulting can accelerate progress. Ideal clients are committed to growth and willing to implement recommendations.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">How does business consulting actually work?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>We start with a discovery process to understand your business, goals, and challenges. Then we develop a custom strategy tailored to your situation. Finally, we support implementation—helping you stay accountable and adjust as needed. It's collaborative, practical, and outcome-focused. We're partners in your growth.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">What does consulting cost?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Pricing varies based on engagement type: one-time strategy sessions ($2,000-$5,000), project-based engagements ($5,000-$25,000), or monthly retainer partnerships ($3,000-$10,000/month). We discuss your budget upfront and create an engagement that works. Many clients find the ROI far exceeds the investment.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">How long does consulting take?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>That depends on your needs. A clarity session might be one day. A strategic planning engagement typically takes 4-8 weeks. Ongoing coaching is a longer-term relationship. We'll discuss timeline upfront and give you realistic expectations about what's achievable in your timeframe.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Do you work with startups or only established businesses?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>We work with both. Startup consulting is actually one of our specialties. We help founders validate ideas, build business models, plan launches, and navigate the unique challenges of starting a company. Many startup founders benefit enormously from experienced outside perspective before making costly mistakes.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Can you help with specific functional areas like marketing or finance?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Absolutely. We specialize in marketing systems, financial planning, operations optimization, and more. We can do deep-dive consulting on any functional area or provide integrated, holistic business consulting across all areas. We also connect you with specialist consultants when needed.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">What if I don't know where to start?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>That's completely normal. The first step is a discovery call where we listen to your situation, understand your goals, and recommend next steps. No pressure. We'll be honest about whether consulting makes sense for you right now, and if it does, what engagement would be best.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Do you serve Lexington KY businesses?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Yes! We're based in Lexington and deeply understand Central Kentucky's business landscape. We serve local businesses in Lexington and throughout Kentucky. We also work with businesses nationwide via video calls and virtual engagements.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">How is your consulting different from other consultants?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>We focus on outcomes, not billable hours. We're integrated with our clients' businesses—we understand marketing, operations, technology, and finance. We're practical and grounded, not theoretical. And we're genuinely invested in your success. You're not just a client; we care about your growth.</p>
				</div>
			</details>

			<details class="faq-item">
				<summary class="faq-question">Can you connect me with other resources I might need?</summary>
				<div class="faq-answer">
					<p>Yes. That's one of our core services. We maintain relationships with accountants, lawyers, contractors, service providers, and other specialists across Central Kentucky. We regularly refer clients to trusted professionals, and we can make introductions to help you build your team.</p>
				</div>
			</details>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Consulting CTA Section -->
	<section class="consulting-cta">
		<div class="cta-content">
			<h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Get Clear on Your Business?</h2>
			<p class="cta-description">Let's talk about your business, your goals, and how strategic consulting can help you grow with clarity and confidence.</p>
			<div class="cta-buttons">
				<button class="cta-primary">Book a Discovery Call</button>
				<button class="cta-secondary">Send a Message</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</RootLayout>

<style>
	/* Hero Section */
	.consulting-hero {
		position: relative;
		min-height: 60vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		overflow: hidden;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	.cosmic-background {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.stars {
		position: absolute;
		width: 2px;
		height: 2px;
		background: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		box-shadow: 100px 100px white, 200px 150px white, 300px 50px white, 450px 200px white,
					550px 100px white, 150px 300px white, 400px 400px white, 600px 300px white,
					700px 150px white, 800px 400px white, 900px 250px white, 200px 500px white,
					700px 500px white, 500px 600px white, 100px 700px white, 800px 700px white,
					300px 800px white;
		animation: twinkle 3s infinite;
	}

	@keyframes twinkle {
		0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; }
		50% { opacity: 1; }
	}

	.nebula {
		position: absolute;
		border-radius: 50%;
		filter: blur(80px);
		opacity: 0.6;
	}

	.nebula-1 {
		width: 400px;
		height: 400px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(163, 0, 255, 0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
		top: 10%;
		left: 10%;
		animation: drift 8s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	.nebula-2 {
		width: 500px;
		height: 500px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
		top: 50%;
		right: 5%;
		animation: drift 10s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
	}

	.nebula-3 {
		width: 350px;
		height: 350px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
		bottom: 10%;
		left: 50%;
		animation: drift 12s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes drift {
		0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0); }
		50% { transform: translate(50px, 50px); }
	}

	.particles {
		position: absolute;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.particles::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		width: 2px;
		height: 2px;
		background: var(--primary-neon);
		border-radius: 50%;
		box-shadow: 100px 200px var(--tertiary-neon), 250px 100px var(--primary-neon),
					150px 400px var(--tertiary-neon), 450px 150px var(--tertiary-neon),
					600px 250px var(--primary-neon), 350px 300px var(--tertiary-neon),
					800px 100px var(--primary-neon), 200px 600px var(--tertiary-neon);
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); opacity: 0.5; }
		50% { transform: translateY(-50px) translateX(30px); opacity: 1; }
	}

	.hero-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 900px;
		gap: 2rem;
		animation: fade-in-up 1s ease-out;
	}

	.consulting-headline {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
		font-weight: 800;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-neon), var(--tertiary-neon), var(--secondary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.consulting-subheadline {
		font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		max-width: 700px;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.hero-pricing {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.price-badge {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tertiary-neon), var(--secondary-neon));
		color: var(--darker-bg);
		border-radius: 50px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.price-subtext {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-style: italic;
	}

	@keyframes fade-in-up {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(30px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

	/* Intro Section */
	.consulting-intro {
		position: relative;
		padding: 5rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.intro-container {
		max-width: 850px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.intro-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-neon), var(--secondary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.intro-text {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	/* Services Section */
	.consulting-services {
		position: relative;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 24, 53, 0.8) 0%, var(--dark-bg) 100%);
		z-index: 2;
	}

	.services-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.services-title {
		font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-neon), var(--primary-neon));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}

	.services-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.service-card-item {
		padding: 2.5rem;
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
		border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
		border-radius: 16px;
		transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.5rem;
	}

	.service-card-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: -100%;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1), transparent);
		transition: left 0.6s ease;
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.service-card-item:hover::before {
		left: 100%;
	}

	.service-card-item:hover {
		background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
		border-color: var(--primary-neon);
		transform: translateY(-12px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.service-card-icon {
		width: 70px;
		height: 70px;
		border-radius: 14px;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.startup-icon {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00ff88, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.6));
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.4);
	}

	.clarity-icon {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-neon), rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.6));
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
	}

	.systems-icon {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-neon), rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.6));
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 110, 0.4);
	}

	.marketing-icon {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tertiary-neon), rgba(163, 0, 255, 0.6));
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(163, 0, 255, 0.4);
	}

	.finance-icon {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8c00, rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.6));
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 140, 0, 0.4);
	}

	.networking-icon {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff00ff, rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.6));
		box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.4);
	}

	.service-card-item h3 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		color: var(--text-primary);
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.service-card-item p {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		line-height: 1.7;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.service-features {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.service-features li {
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		padding-left: 1.5rem;
